{"tid":591658,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"為何10年過去, 我仍放唔低妳?","createTime":"2018-03-13T17:38:46.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-14T04:11:59.000Z","uid":107053,"like":8,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"73dd0bdd4371f1b4b4e2fa7503b7bad845608be8","tid":591658,"uid":107053,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-13T17:38:46.000Z","msg":"10年前, 即2008年, 同樣係3月, 妳靜靜的離開, 去一個我去唔到的地方。10年過去, 妳在天的那一方生活何好?<br />\n10年來, 每當諗起妳, 眼框的淚珠總不期然滾出來, 你狠心的拋下, 我將所有扛上。這就是妳所說的「細路仔」嗎？<br />\n妳走後3年, 台灣有一個組合叫五月天, 他們有一首歌叫「我不願讓你一個人」, 這歌仿佛是我的故事, 這7年來, 我不斷loop這首歌, 每晚聽著這歌入睡, 聽到有手機無電, 是我的固執嗎?<br />\n我多麼多麼希望一切重新來過, 可惜世上沒有後悔藥。如果上天允許, 聽聽我的祈願, 只求妳有快樂人生。<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/38lcQsEMGrk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F38lcQsEMGrk&d=AuF%2BR4E1NNtI17gjFGCCJzM0pwszV1jUpWwTgNsMWwc%3D&h=efcd1e70\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/38lcQsEMGrk</a>"},{"pid":"9f34ce5be302648be9de0f660af463aad0d8a984","tid":591658,"uid":75359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-13T17:40:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"719c32e8af8fda8f50e23708cbe174685364e2c8","tid":591658,"uid":95499,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-13T17:52:52.000Z","msg":"好好咁生活，當你地重聚嗰日，佢會笑住咁嚟迎接你"},{"pid":"80af60f41aacd2d9c901f0b979cdcda06062cd8e","tid":591658,"uid":5984,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-13T17:59:54.000Z","msg":"佢無狠心拋下你 我諗佢都唔想咁<br />\n節哀順變啦樓主"},{"pid":"a9f4c3c50183616388be93a9ff68ff68c3697850","tid":591658,"uid":107053,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"719c32e8af8fda8f50e23708cbe174685364e2c8","tid":591658,"uid":95499,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-13T17:52:52.000Z","msg":"好好咁生活，當你地重聚嗰日，佢會笑住咁嚟迎接你"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-13T18:06:30.000Z","msg":"其實我真係幾期待重聚的一天, 但我未諗到我哋開口第一句應該講咩？"},{"pid":"165816d45055eafce8437b2acb77d1ba22f021c3","tid":591658,"uid":160781,"like":0,"dis